      <font size=3 color="008000"><b><a name="cont">Listing Fees &amp; Other Charges:</b></font><br><br>
      <b>Per item sale fee sliding scale:</b><br>This allows you to establish a fixed or sliding scale
      of values or percentages to charge the seller, depending on the price of the item they sold.  The
      edit box labeled "Segment" is where you put the <i>minimum</i> value (dollar amount) the charge in
      the <i>value</i> box applies to.  Note that you can put either a dollar amount (without a dollar
      sign [$] ) or a percentage (with a trailing percent [%] sign).  You may add or delete segments at
      any point in the scale.  If you want one value to apply to all sales, have only one entry with "0"
      for the segment and the charge for the value.  All sales, regardless of price, would be charged that fee.
      <br><br>
